# Tabs — Visual Spec

## CSS Classes

- `.acko-tabs` — base wrapper, `w-full`
- `.acko-tabs-list` — flex container for tab buttons
- `.acko-tab` — base tab button, `inline-flex items-center`, `gap: var(--scale-8)`, no border, bg-transparent

## Variants

### Underline
- `.acko-tabs-list-underline` — `border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle)`, `position: relative`
- `.acko-tab-underline` — padding `var(--scale-8) var(--scale-16)`, `margin-bottom: -1px`, position relative
- Active indicator via `::after` pseudo-element:
  - `background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-primary), transparent)`
  - `height: 2px`, `border-radius: 1px`, positioned at bottom
  - `transition: background 250ms var(--ease-in-out-cubic)`
- Active text: `--color-primary`

### Underline (top indicator)
- `.acko-tabs-list-underline-top` — `border-top` instead of `border-bottom`
- `::after` positioned at top instead of bottom

### Pill
- `.acko-tabs-list-pill` — `background: var(--color-tab-pill-bg)`, `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`, `padding: var(--scale-4)`, `width: fit-content`
- `.acko-tab-pill` — `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`, padding `var(--scale-4) var(--scale-16)`
- Active (light): `background: var(--color-primary-subtle)` (purple-100), `color: var(--color-primary)`, `--shadow-sm`
- Active (dark): `background: var(--color-primary-subtle)` (purple-900), `color: var(--color-on-primary)` (white)

### Navigation (bottom tabs)
- `.acko-tabs-list-navigation` — `background: var(--color-card-bg)`, `border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle)`, `justify-content: space-around`
- `.acko-tab-navigation` — `flex-col`, icon `var(--scale-24)`, label `--font-caption-size`, `min-width: var(--scale-64)`
- Active (light): `background: var(--color-primary-subtle)`, `color: var(--color-primary)`, `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`
- Active (dark): `background: var(--color-primary)`, `color: var(--color-on-primary)`, `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`

### Enclosed
- `.acko-tab-enclosed` — `border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle)`, no bottom border
- Active: `--color-card-bg` background

## Sizes
- `.acko-tab-sm` — `--font-caption-size`, padding `var(--scale-4) var(--scale-12)`
- `.acko-tab-md` — `--font-body-sm-size`, padding `var(--scale-8) var(--scale-16)`

## Icon
- `.acko-tab-icon` — `var(--scale-16) × var(--scale-16)`, shrink-0
- Navigation variant icons: `var(--scale-24)`

## Token Usage

| Token | Role |
|-------|------|
| `--color-primary` | Active underline gradient center, active text, navigation active |
| `--color-text-secondary` | Inactive tab text |
| `--color-text-primary` | Active pill text |
| `--color-tab-pill-bg` | Pill container background |
| `--color-primary-subtle` | Active pill fill (purple-100 light / purple-900 dark) |
| `--color-card-bg` | Enclosed active bg, navigation bar bg |
| `--color-border-subtle` | List border, enclosed tab border, navigation border-top |
| `--shadow-sm` | Active pill shadow |

## Transitions
All variants: `color 200ms var(--ease-in-out-cubic)`, pill adds `all 200ms var(--ease-in-out-cubic)`

## Props (React)
- `variant`: `"underline" | "pill" | "enclosed" | "navigation"`
- `indicatorPosition`: `"top" | "bottom"` (underline only)
- `size`: `"sm" | "md"`
- `fullWidth`: boolean
- `items`: `TabItem[]` with optional `icon` ReactNode
